в”Ӯ                                                                                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ Core keys:                                                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   j/k or arrows  Move selection                                                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   h/l             Mode-aware lateral nav (board lanes, graph peers, insights pane focus)         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   Ctrl+d/Ctrl+u   Jump down/up by 10 rows                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   PgUp/PgDn       Jump by 10 rows                                                                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   Home/End         Jump to top/bottom                                                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   /               Board/History/Graph/Insights: search (n/N match cycling)                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   Tab              Toggle list/detail focus                                                      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   J/K              Detail: navigate blockers/dependents (board/graph/insights)                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   b/i/g/h          Toggle board/insights/graph/history                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   Enter            Return to main detail pane                                                    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   o/c/r/a          Filter open/closed/ready/all                                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   s                Main: cycle sort | Board: cycle grouping | Insights: cycle panel              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   ?                Toggle help overlay                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   Esc              Back from mode (or clear filter, then quit confirm in main)                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   q                Main: quit | Non-main: return to main                                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   Ctrl+C           Quit immediately                                                              в”Ӯ
